# ENV-BASED CONFIGURATION

## RULES
**❌ NEVER**: `System.getenv("KEY")` directly  
**✅ ALWAYS**: `@Value("${app.key:default}")`

**Why**: Testable, mockable, profile-specific, Docker/K8s compatible

## STRUCTURE
- application.yml → defaults
- application-{profile}.yml → env-specific (dev/test/prod)
- @Profile → conditional beans
- @Value → `@Value("${key:defaultValue}")`

## CRITICAL
- NO secrets in code/git → environment variables
- ALWAYS provide fallback defaults
- NO System.getenv() directly
